  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Reload Archive</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page task  - topic-topic task-task \" id=\"loio4ea2c6995a2f4f57e10000000a42189e\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Reload Archive</h1><div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\"></p>\n<div class=\"section context\"><span id=\"steps\" class=\"anchor\"></span><div class=\"tasklabel\"><h2 class=\"sectiontitle tasklabel\">Context</h2></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The archived user log is reloaded again into the database. </p>\n</div>\n<section class=\"section procedure\"><span id=\"steps\" class=\"anchor\"></span><div class=\"ol steps tasklabel\"><h2 class=\"sectiontitle tasklabel\">Procedure</h2></div><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Financial Supply Chain Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Treasury and Risk Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Basic Functions</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Market Data Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Datafeed</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Usage Log</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Reload Archive</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>.</span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Archive Administration: Reload Archive Sessions</span> screen appears.</span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Enter the variant needed to start the archiving program as well as the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Archive Selection</span>, the\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Start Date</span>, and the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Spool Parameters</span>.</span>\n</li><li class=\"li step\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Create Job</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> to reload the file.</span>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
